The paper proposes a novel representation for 2D human body, which involves joint learning of human pose and shape. Therefore, it is likely to belong to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques, such as convolutional neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
